    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a fair summary. i'm curious though, when looking at the modeling for these things, is there a consensus on whether the environmental benefits actually outweigh the socio-economic costs? like, is the policy generally seen as a successful path forward or just a temporary fix?",
